<h2>  Indus Nexus Privacy Policy </h2>
<p> 

This document entails all the necessary information that we collect from you and share. You will also get a brief idea about the privacy guidelines, so that you can be fully informed as to how best you can use this website. In this document Indus Nexus will be referred to as 'we', 'us', 'our' and 'ours’. Our visitors/users/customers/advertisers/publishers will be referred to as 'theirs', 'them', 'you' and 'yours’.   
</p><br /><br /><h3> The Information we collect </h3><p>
We collect both personal and business related information of our customers, advertisers and publishers. The information is collected for the sole purpose of smooth business and payment transactions. Your information will be kept confidential. We also expect that you provide us the correct details and not otherwise as it will lead to unnecessary altercation.
</p>
<h3> Sharing your information  </h3><p>
In some specific business scenarios, there might be chances that your information will be used for a constructive purpose or it might be for a promotional purpose, or for a business that you might be interested in. Sharing your information might turn out to be beneficial. It entirely depends upon you whether you want to share your information or not. </p>
<h3> Sign-up forms  </h3>
<p>
When you want to officially trade with Indus Nexus, then you will be provided with a sign-up form, after filling and signing up, it will be officially declared that you will be trading with Indus Nexus business norms. We encourage you to provide only correct information, while filling up the sign-up form. If we find any of your information provided is false, then we can take the necessary action.</p>
<h3> Opt-out Option</h3>
<p>
Indus Nexus provides an option wherein a publisher or advertiser can opt-out, which means they can withdraw their services from Indus Nexus, as they doesn’t want to trade further with us. There will be a methodical process that will be carried out for the process of opting out, so that we can have a clear view as to what was the specific reason.
</p>
<h3> Information Security</h3>
<p>
Indus Nexus has a security systems set in place. With the necessary security software’s being implemented, your information will be secured. If, due to any technical malfunction the systems are not working properly, then we should not be held responsible. Our technical team will of course fix the problem as soon as possible.
</p>
<h3> Privacy Policy of Advertisers and Publishers </h3>
<p>
Both Advertisers and Publishers who are working with us will be having their own privacy policies to act upon. It would be good for both advertisers and publishers to exchange their privacy policies, so that there can be proper business decorum. We hence expect both advertisers and publishers to abide by their respective privacy policies.
</p>
<h3> Links to other Websites </h3>
<p>
Indus Nexus will display links of many other sites on Indus Nexus website. However, we are in no way responsible for their ads and content. Any of the user/customer/advertiser/publisher who visits these links are at their own risk. We connect and accept links only because of the fact that these businesses are in tune with our business type.    
</p>
<h3> Notify Changes </h3>
<p>
If there are any changes to our privacy policy document, then it will be notified to our customers, advertisers and publishers. However, we would also encourage our valued customers, advertisers and publishers to visit the privacy policy page often, so that they will be better equipped with our policies and hence can work in a harmonious manner.
  


</p>    
